<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Subscription Expiring</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #f59e0b;">Subscription Expiring Soon</h1>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>Your <strong>{{planName}}</strong> subscription for <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> will expire in <strong>{{daysLeft}} day(s)</strong>.</p>
  <p>To continue enjoying all the features, please ensure your payment method is up to date.</p>
  <p>
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #f59e0b; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
      Manage Subscription
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Digital Directory Team</p>
</body>
</html>
